plt.xlabel("Total Bill")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](visualization_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-29-1.png){width=90%}
:::
:::

:::

#### One Continuous Variable and One Categorical Variable

::: panel-tabset
## R


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
